{"tid":2362117,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係弼街咩stm group interview?","createTime":"2021-01-11T08:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T07:15:54.000Z","uid":128752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a286d1aebe97f0adc8edd25c00bda38b36938f","tid":2362117,"uid":128752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:24:48.000Z","msg":"上到去見到勁多人目測30人左右<br />\n唔係正常office係一排排長枱<br />\n門口附近有6張枱一對一interview<br />\n除左我都有4-5個都in緊<br />\n個經理會係張白紙介紹係做咩marketing工作<br />\n話咩有前線亦有back office<br />\n但係聽完都係唔知做乜9<br />\n得左會有個一星期無paid既training <br />\n想問係咪呃人傳銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b5db4fc75d746c324274e035c471c53c94d6cc","tid":2362117,"uid":85774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"一排排長枱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定係"},{"pid":"a685eb9354ca7bec748922ff69e90c9bffa48ebf","tid":2362117,"uid":347590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38b5db4fc75d746c324274e035c471c53c94d6cc","tid":2362117,"uid":85774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"一排排長枱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f9cb1717f68cc2592c129288564ad3667112e8","tid":2362117,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:15:05.000Z","msg":"以下呢間？<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span class=\"green\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BUtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=af91bf3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BUtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=5c9379bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BUtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=55c1b587\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXuxBB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXuxBB7.png&h=dffa07b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85769fd3bbe4ff6f3d6ff631dd8a9f4b06903096","tid":2362117,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"巴打最尾有冇中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}